0.04

        - default encoding for TSVRPC is Base64.
        - added benchmark code.
        - fixed docs

0.03

        - [INCOMPATIBLE CHANGE] TSVRPC::Client->call() now returns plain array instead of TSVRPC::Response for better performance.
        - remove fucking unused code.

